A Spined body is a members-only piece of Ranged armour. To wear a spined body, the player must have at least 40 Defence, 40 Ranged, and have completed The Fremennik Trials quest. Stat-wise, it is identical to the Gilded d'hide body.

To obtain a spined body, a player can either bring 3 dagannoth hides, 1 flattened hide, and 10,000 coins to Sigli the Huntsman in Rellekka, receive it as a drop from Dagannoth Supreme, or trade with another player.

This body can be stored in the armour case of a costume room, as part of the Spined armour set. Ultimate Ironmen will be unable to retrieve individual pieces until the full set is stored.
